title: Boots Randolph
description:
Ok , Heres a collection of ripps from my personal Boots Randolph collection.

Enjoy

Please join the crusade to remaster and preserve old vinyls that were never published in cd.

This aint like stealing music CDs put out and manufactured by the corporate entity...this is about preserving what the corporate entity wont put out in cd. Once the vinyls are gone, the music is gone forever....
think about that.
